WEBVTT

00:09:28.478 --> 00:09:30.387
i kad smo to završili,

00:09:30.387 --> 00:09:32.371
morali smo da uzmemo u obzir
svih 46 tomova

00:09:32.371 --> 00:09:34.224
jer u nekim slučajevima autizma

00:09:34.224 --> 00:09:36.680
može nedostajati jedan tom.

00:09:36.680 --> 00:09:38.990
Morali smo da budemo sitničavi

00:09:38.990 --> 00:09:41.310
i počeli smo da otvaramo knjige,

00:09:41.310 --> 00:09:43.190
i u nekim slučajevima genetska promena

00:09:43.190 --> 00:09:44.578
je bila suptilnija.

00:09:44.578 --> 00:09:47.764
Negde je nedostajao samo jedan pasus

00:09:47.764 --> 00:09:51.042
ili, još suptilnije,

00:09:51.042 --> 00:09:52.734
samo jedno slovo,

00:09:52.734 --> 00:09:55.536
jedno od tri milijarde slova

00:09:55.536 --> 00:09:57.810
koje se promenilo,

00:09:57.810 --> 00:09:59.407
a ipak je imalo dubok uticaj

00:09:59.407 --> 00:10:01.320
na moždane funkcije